AXIOS
it is a promise based HTTP client for the browserr and node.js
-make XMLHttpRequests from brrowser
-make http requst from  node
-supports the rpomise api

Automatic request body serialization to:
-JSON(application/json)
-Multipart/FormData(multipart/formdata)
-URL encoded from (application/x-www-form-urlencoded)
